import { Button } from "@chakra-ui/button";
import { Flex, Text } from "@chakra-ui/layout";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function Nav() {
  return (
    <Flex
      p="30px"
      background="0"
      alignItems="center"
      
      w="100%"
      m="0 auto"
      maxW="1367px"
    >
      <Text color="#454545" mr="20px">
        Quem somos
      </Text>
      <Link to="/Login">
        <Button
          _hover={{}}
          width="89px"
          height="35px"
          background="#fff"
          boxShadow="0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19)"
          borderRadius="45px"
        >
          Logar
        </Button>
      </Link>
    </Flex>
  );
}
